- Gutega amatwi umwana;
- Kuganira na we kenshi;
- Kumusomera no kumubwira udukuru tw’abana;
- Gushishikariza abanagukina no gutembera ngo bamenye 
  ibibakikije;
- Kumva no gusubiza ibibazo by’abana no kugirana nabo ibigan- iro;
- Kumushishikariza guhimba udukino tw’abana no gushushanya;
- Kubuza umwana kureba televiziyo mu gihe kitari ngombwa 
  n’igihe cy’ibiganiro birimo amashusho akanganye;
- Kumushishikariza kugira imyitwarire myiza no kumushyiriraho 
  
  ibyo atagomba kurenga mu rwego rwo kumutoza imico myiza;
- Kumwereka urukundo buri gihe;niba hari ahantu ha ho kwigira    
  imikino y’abana, umwana agomba kujyanwayo mu rwego rwo  kumumenyereza
  gahunda y’ishuri.
